@startuml
title AUTH.RF001 - Login de Usuário

actor User

boundary Frontend
control AuthResolver
control AuthService
control JWTService
control BCryptService
database PostgreSQL

User -> Frontend : Acessa tela de login

Frontend -> User : Exibe formulário\n(username,password)

User -> Frontend : Preenche credenciais

Frontend -> AuthResolver : mutation login(username,password)

AuthResolver -> AuthService : authenticate(credentials)

AuthService -> PostgreSQL : buscarUsuario(username)

PostgreSQL --> AuthService : dadosUsuario

alt Usuário encontrado

    AuthService -> BCryptService : validarSenha(password, hash)

    BCryptService --> AuthService : resultado

    alt Senha válida

        AuthService -> AuthService : verificarContaAtiva()

        alt Conta ativa

            AuthService -> AuthService : resetarTentativasFalhas()

            AuthService -> JWTService : gerarToken(userId,role)

            JWTService --> AuthService : JWT(24h)

            AuthService --> AuthResolver : token + userData

            AuthResolver --> Frontend : Login OK

            Frontend --> User : Dashboard + Token

        else Conta bloqueada/inativa

            AuthService --> AuthResolver : Erro Conta Inativa

            AuthResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 403

            Frontend --> User : Acesso negado

        end

    else Senha inválida

        AuthService -> AuthService : incrementarTentativas()

        AuthService --> AuthResolver : Erro autenticação

        AuthResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 401

        Frontend --> User : Credenciais inválidas

    end

else Usuário inexistente

    AuthService --> AuthResolver : Usuário não encontrado

    AuthResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 401

    Frontend --> User : Login inválido

end

@enduml